NAME

  Lingua::EN::Sentence 

DESCRIPTION
  
  Module for splitting text into sentences.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install
   
   or
   
   perl Build.PL
   build
   build test
   build install
   

MAINTAINER

This project was originated by Shlomo Yona. Currently  maintained
by Kim Ryan
